      "content": "thanks. can you make it a bit more personal? like, acknowledge that they put in a lot of work for the technical assessment and the final interviews? also, maybe add something about how the competition was really intense this time around, just to soften the blow. something like 'we had a massive pool of incredibly talented people to choose from.'",
